{"tid":2487710,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"東華三院國安教育資源套指社會事件是恐怖活動 反送中屬「不法分子顛覆政權」 外部勢力干預","createTime":"2021-04-13T17:54:54.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-13T23:21:51.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"fb0b88a3f8148d44d80f52f5365b9ce1fb12e9fd","tid":2487710,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:54:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/-EYiV_Cq6gejJF11t3hUkBanVgA=/802x293/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FEQCRMUYVFFO3DJ5WZ2SVR2QZQ.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F-EYiV_Cq6gejJF11t3hUkBanVgA%3D%2F802x293%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFEQCRMUYVFFO3DJ5WZ2SVR2QZQ.JPG&h=3e5e5ec0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/2KO2IFDA1ezuxKzQhsyGEe-EibY=/802x596/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TVIFNXNL7VHNXO3V4PAVL3C5QY.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F2KO2IFDA1ezuxKzQhsyGEe-EibY%3D%2F802x596%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTVIFNXNL7VHNXO3V4PAVL3C5QY.JPG&h=dc6590c8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n開辦18間中學和14間小學的東華三院，去年底推出《國安教育參考資源套》，內容一面倒緊跟官方口徑。《蘋果》發現，資源套指過去香港發生的事件「並非只是社會運動」，而是「不法分子企圖分裂國家、顛覆政權、進行恐怖活動」，又使用「百年恥辱，割地賠款」等字眼。有教育學者質疑前者說法並無任何證據，後者更鼓動師生仇恨外國，批評東華三院「跟足政權口吻」表忠。<br />\n<br />\n東華三院早前向屬校派發《國安教育參考資源套》，長逾百頁，由教育科主管吳奇壎任顧問，列出從憲制、法律、執行等不同角度的問與答。<br />\n<br />\n其中一問「成立《國安法》對香港社會有何逼切性？」的答案提及，過去香港發生的事件「並非只是社會運動，不法分子企圖分裂國家、顛覆政權、進行恐怖活動，也有外部勢力的干預」，更指香港沒有法例防範、制止和懲治，故「中央政府有逼切性作出決定」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/H4RWD65GTVAYPKU5HSQXYNCXTI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FH4RWD65GTVAYPKU5HSQXYNCXTI%2F&d=anIIoOx73pQIzJB4hJH11JgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=5adf54aa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210414%2FH4RWD65GTVAYPKU5HSQXYNCXTI%2F&h=a23ca9a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210414/H4RWD65GTVAYPKU5HSQXYNCXTI/</a>"},{"pid":"1eaa4638c2be5ee49c727af06b59707ea357ebde","tid":2487710,"uid":74764,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T17:56:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5317418d80e25132cc74db8e0471c003cd74b6c3","tid":2487710,"uid":393145,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T18:11:58.000Z","msg":"咁撚驚外國侵略咪去打外國囉 拉外國人囉 國安法依家係鎮壓自己百姓喎 關外國侵略撚事咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4249705b7fabc81a79ee95230bd26178836cdef9","tid":2487710,"uid":19527,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T18:19:12.000Z","msg":"百年恥辱係恥辱在自己廢撚到閪咁啊<br />\n咩北洋水師不堪一擊<br />\n又自居天朝大國當其他國家係蠻夷"},{"pid":"efe46462434e30ee2fe2ac34829862a60edbb9dc","tid":2487710,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:17:37.000Z","msg":"好想知中國1949年後有乜愛國運動？<br />\n1949年前有乜係顛覆國家嘅恐怖主義活動？"},{"pid":"4c2188b39a09c20a3f41569b996fc572bcae6481","tid":2487710,"uid":233905,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"efe46462434e30ee2fe2ac34829862a60edbb9dc","tid":2487710,"uid":79410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:17:37.000Z","msg":"好想知中國1949年後有乜愛國運動？<br />\n1949年前有乜係顛覆國家嘅恐怖主義活動？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-13T20:21:21.000Z","msg":"共產黨咪顛覆咗中華民國政權 而且仲大規模對中華民國進行恐怖主義活動<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23f63e02eeba17d1bb336f0d288ca295cbd04266","tid":2487710,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":0,